ion and transportation of sand beyond permissible hours. Meanwhile, Chandrapur police invoked MCOCA against a sand mafia gang involved in murder and other unlawful activities.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/allied-industries/yavatmals-illegal-sand-mining-racket-exposed-major-seizures-and-arrests/129388582?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-122249/129388582.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "allied-industries"}]}